  "technicalDetails": "<p>Number of Blueprints: 1 Actor Blueprint for the Gizmo, 1 Blueprint for the screen widget and 1 Blueprint to fly around.</p><p>Input: Mouse:</p><ul><li>Left Mouse Button: Select static mesh actor to edit. Select gizmo to transform the selected mesh.</li><li>Space Key: Switch between transform modes (location, rotation, scale)</li><li>M: Cycle between global and local axis translate.</li></ul><p>Network Replicated: No. Dealing with changes made by the gizmo must be done by you.</p><p>Supported Development Platforms: Windows, Linux, MAC</p><p>Supported Target Build Platforms: Windows, Linux, MAC (Any platform with mouse support)</p><p>Documentation: <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id&#61;1138z2En4tJi3lJwib_5LfDaxMi7Xo-mF\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://drive.google.com/open?id&#61;1138z2En4tJi3lJwib_5LfDaxMi7Xo-mF</a></p><p>Important/Additional Notes:</p>",
